{"tid":2243111,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[25歲以上入] 以前搭地鐵有冇人知究竟咩嚟","createTime":"2020-10-14T13:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T01:00:52.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f63e4653cfc622aa4654de7aa175e3ca2b25fd0f","tid":2243111,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"睇另一篇關於記憶嘅post有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家27歲 2-3歲嗰時有次同親戚出街食完飯 仲好記得夜晚9點幾喺旺角搭地鐵返屋企 等等吓車成個月台突然勁嘈 見到有抽唔知咩車都幾快咁飛過 (唔係普通車 車身好似黑黑哋色) 個feel勁恐怖 嚇到攬住屋企人喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住到6歲前都喺太子同葵興遇到類似咁嘅車 時間唔定 日頭都有 一知道即刻合埋眼同&quot;um&quot;耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後咁多年就冇見過 夜晚好夜嗰時不時有啲工程車過站 多數黃色頭 不過把聲唔同之餘冇咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網已經搵唔返幾歲嗰時見到嘅車 個樣最似就係東鐵豬車 不過明明係喺旺角地鐵站見到 唔係火車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇25歲以上嘅人知咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d07bc88ab98b6dabfd21b413e3ada19f0d1b8c7","tid":2243111,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"直通貨運火車"},{"pid":"58ff7b4e420cd733ad3ee864c37d4b95ce0bf746","tid":2243111,"uid":55851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"狄波拉效應"},{"pid":"35bf67f98bb9e6053e120274c0f68fbda5b18dbf","tid":2243111,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.breadtrip.com/trips/2387220298/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.breadtrip.com%2Ftrips%2F2387220298%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3397d7b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.breadtrip.com/trips/2387220298/</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪呢種<img src=\"/asset